* {{ill|Ōtsuka Kofun (Sukagawa)|ja|大塚古墳 (須賀川市)|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Komagata Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|駒形大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nakagawa, Tochigi|ja|那須郡那珂川町|12=draft|12=draft}}, Tochigi Prefecture, part of the {{ill|Nasu Ogawa Kofun Cluster|ja|那須小川古墳群|12=draft|12=draft}}. Designated a national historic site. * {{ill|Tomatsuri Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|戸祭大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Utsunomiya|ja|宇都宮市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Tochigi Prefecture. * {{ill|Shimoguri Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|下栗大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Utsunomiya, Tochigi Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtsuka Kofun (Kawajima)|ja|大塚古墳 (川島町)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Kawajima|ja|川島町|12=draft|12=draft}}, Saitama Prefecture. * {{ill|Hōfun Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|方墳|1=Square Kofun大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Saitama City|ja|さいたま市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Saitama Prefecture. * {{ill|Noge Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|野毛大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Setagaya|ja|世田谷区|12=draft|12=draft}}, Tokyo. * {{ill|Unoki Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|鵜木大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Ōta, Tokyo|ja|大田区雪谷大塚町|12=draft|12=draft}}, Tokyo. * {{ill|Miyazaki Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|宮崎大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Miyamae-ku, Kawasaki|ja|川崎市宮前区宮崎|12=draft|12=draft}}, Kanagawa Prefecture. * {{ill|Hiruiōzuka Kofun|ja|昼飯大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Ōgaki|ja|大垣市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Gifu Prefecture. Designated a national historic site. * {{ill|Sōkei Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|宗慶大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Motosu|ja|本巣市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Gifu Prefecture. * {{ill|Shidami Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|志段味大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Moriyama-ku, Nagoya|ja|名古屋市守山区|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. * {{ill|Toyota Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|豊田大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Toyota|ja|豊田市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. Excavated {{ill|sue ware|ja|須恵器|1=Sue pottery|12=draft|12=draft}} designated as an important cultural property. * {{ill|Terado Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|寺戸大塚古墳|1=Terado Ōtsuka Kofun|lt=Terado Ōtsuka Kofun|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Mukō|ja|向日市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Kyoto Prefecture. Designated a national historic site. * {{ill|Ōtsuka Kofun (Toyonaka)|ja|桜塚古墳群 (豊中市)#大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Toyonaka|ja|豊中市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Osaka Prefecture. * {{ill|Kariguri Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|軽里大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Habikino|ja|羽曳野市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Osaka Prefecture. Officially designated by the {{ill|Imperial Household Agency|ja|宮内庁|12=draft|12=draft}} as the tomb of {{ill|Yamato Takeru|lt=Yamato Takeru no Mikoto|ja|ヤマトタケル|de|Yamatotakeru|fr|Yamato Takeru|ko|야마토타케루|ja|日本武尊白鳥陵|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Higaida Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|東田大塚古墳|1=Higaida Ōtsuka Kofun|lt=Higaida Ōtsuka Kofun|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Sakurai, Nara|ja|桜井市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Nara Prefecture. Part of the {{ill|Makimuku Kofun Cluster|ja|纒向古墳群|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Nakayama Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|中山大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Tenri|ja|天理市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Nara Prefecture. * {{ill|Yanagimoto Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|柳本大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Tenri, Nara Prefecture. * {{ill|Kuroda Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|黒田大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Tawaramoto|ja|磯城郡田原本町|12=draft|12=draft}}, Nara Prefecture. * {{ill|Musa Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|牟佐大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Okayama|ja|岡山市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Okayama Prefecture. Designated a national historic site. * {{ill|Yata Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|箭田大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Kurashiki|ja|倉敷市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Okayama Prefecture. Designated a national historic site. * {{ill|Imajuku Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|今宿大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nishi-ku, Fukuoka|ja|福岡市西区|12=draft|12=draft}}, Fukuoka Prefecture. Part of the {{ill|Imajuku Kofun Cluster|ja|今宿古墳群|12=draft|12=draft}}. Designated a national historic site. * {{ill|Tanushimaru Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|田主丸大塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Tanushimaru, Fukuoka|ja|浮羽郡田主丸町|12=draft|12=draft}}, Fukuoka Prefecture. Part of the {{ill|Tanushimaru Kofun Cluster|ja|田主丸古墳群|12=draft|12=draft}}. Designated a national historic site.
