13=User:Immanuelle/Yanagimoto Ōtsuka Kofun|qq=}} - Located in Tenri, Nara Prefecture. * {{ill|Kuroda Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|黒田大塚古墳|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuroda Ōtsuka Kofun|qq=}} - Located in {{ill|Tawaramoto|ja|磯城郡田原本町|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tawaramoto|qq=}}, Nara Prefecture. * [[:en:Musa Ōtsuka Kofun|Musa Ōtsuka Kofun]] - Located in [[:en:Okayama|Okayama]], Okayama Prefecture. Designated a national historic site. * [[:en:Yata Ōtsuka Kofun|Yata Ōtsuka Kofun]] - Located in [[:en:Kurashiki|Kurashiki]], Okayama Prefecture. Designated a national historic site. * {{ill|Imajuku Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|今宿大塚古墳|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Imajuku Ōtsuka Kofun|qq=}} - Located in {{ill|Nishi-ku, Fukuoka|ja|福岡市西区|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nishi-ku, Fukuoka|qq=}}, Fukuoka Prefecture. Part of the {{ill|Imajuku Kofun Cluster|ja|今宿古墳群|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Imajuku Kofun Cluster|qq=}}. Designated a national historic site. * {{ill|Tanushimaru Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|田主丸大塚古墳|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanushimaru Ōtsuka Kofun|qq=}} - Located in {{ill|Tanushimaru, Fukuoka|ja|浮羽郡田主丸町|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanushimaru, Fukuoka|qq=}}, Fukuoka Prefecture. Part of the {{ill|Tanushimaru Kofun Cluster|ja|田主丸古墳群|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanushimaru Kofun Cluster|qq=}}. Designated a national historic site.
